Municipal Manager Bheki Khenisa said the Graspan Reservoir is gradually filling up. Residents in Mhluzi, Extensions 2,4,5,6,7,8,23, parts of Aerorand, Gholfsig and Roberts Estate will only have water when the water levels at the Graspan Reservoir is enough to supply water to households. The interruption of water supply is due to a pipeline failure during the weekend.